author: Alastair Gale
title: North Korea and China Tout Ties at Military Parade - WSJ
text:
SEOUL—North Korea and China played up their ties as a senior Beijing official passed a letter from Chinese President Xi Jinping to Kim Jong Un calling for closer relations and stood alongside the North Korean leader at a military parade in Pyongyang on Saturday.
